	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />During a session where it's malfunctioning, try some other games without physically disturbing the cartridge. This will run them in the same temperature and edge connector environment so that if it's the hardware, it will occur again. You might also verify the programs you're running on the PowerPak, in case the copies on your card are corrupt.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


